9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Forgotten | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Seoul, South Korea, 1997. When the young but extremely anxious student Jin-seok, his parents and his successful older brother Yoo-seok move to a new home, mysterious and frightening events begin to happen around them, unexplained events that threaten to ruin their seemingly happy lives. Unable to understand what is happening, Jin-seok wonders if he is losing his mind."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106903/forgotten"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Forgotten"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Seoul, South Korea, 1997. When the young but extremely anxious student Jin-seok, his parents and his successful older brother Yoo-seok move to a new home, mysterious and frightening events begin to happen around them, unexplained events that threaten to ruin their seemingly happy lives. Unable to understand what is happening, Jin-seok wonders if he is losing his mind."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106903/forgotten"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cBgj41y1RvmW1zJCEX0uNWL0UjW.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Forgotten"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Seoul, South Korea, 1997. When the young but extremely anxious student Jin-seok, his parents and his successful older brother Yoo-seok move to a new home, mysterious and frightening events begin to happen around them, unexplained events that 